<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA614_03_IH_0003_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema614_01.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ena614_03">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="3" lang="y">
          <span lang="y">그림을 보고 축구공 수와 전체 공 수의 비를 써 보세요.</span>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="ball flex justify_center align_end">
          <div class="ball_box flex gap_8 align_center justify_center">
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
            </div>
            <span class="fs_32">:</span>
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="10"></math-field>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="ball_box flex gap_8 align_center justify_center">
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field>
            </div>
            <span class="fs_32">:</span>
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="6"></math-field>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 해설 -->
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve"></div>
              <p>
                전체 공 10개 중 축구공은 3개이므로 축구공 수와 전체 공 수의 비는 3 : 10입니다. <br />
                전체 공 6개 중 축구공은 4개이므로 축구공 수와 전체 공 수의 비는 4 : 6입니다.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
